{{> header_standard}}
<div id="banner" class="row expanded">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="column">
      <h2 id="page-title">{{name}}{{#if also}}, {{also}}{{/if}}</h2>
      <p class="subheading">
        We would love you to attend our wedding celebrations.
      </p>
      <div class="faces">Deborah &amp; Woody</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="main" class="row expanded">
  <div class="row">
    <div id="content" class="column">
        <h3 class="text-center">
          <em>Wedding of</em><br>
          <strong>Andrew Goodricke</strong> &amp; <strong>Deborah Steele</strong>
        </h3>
        <h3 class="text-center">
          Saturday <strong>9th September</strong> 2017, 10:30am<br>
          <em>at</em> <span data-magellan><a href="#map"><strong>Sconner Down</strong>, Cornwall (Map)</a> &mdash; <span title="Sat-Nav Friendly Postcode">PL11&nbsp;3ES</span></span>.
        </h3>
        {{#unless rsvp}}
        <h2 class="text-center" data-magellan>
          Please <a href="#rsvp">RSVP</a> asap.
        </h2>
        {{/unless}}

        <h2>
          The Idea
        </h2>
        <p>
          We want to make the most of having friends and family all together in one spot, so we're thinking of our wedding as a camping weekend with a ceremony thrown in.
        </p>
        <p>
          We hope you can relax, catch up, and enjoy hanging out together.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is very much a DIY wedding without any staff to help, and without too many limitations regarding noise levels or curfews.
        </p>
        <p>
          The evening party will be Bring-a-bottle!
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="/">More information can be found on the main page.</a>
        </p>

        <h2>
          Itinerary <em>(subject to change)</em>
        </h2>
        <h3>
          Friday 8th September
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Arrival at Sconner Down any time from midday.
          </li>
          <li>
          If you would like to help us prepare the site, that would be most welcome, but obviously this part isn't mandatory!
        </li>
        <li>
          Camping on site with us is encouraged (and free) however there are <a href="/#accommodation">other local accommodation options</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Campers should bring some food to have in the evening (there is a fire and a kitchen area), and something for breakfast.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>
        Saturday 9th September
      </h3>
      <ul class="itinary">
        <li>
          <span>10:30am</span> &mdash; Arrival
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>11am</span> &mdash; Wedding Ceremony
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>12noon</span> &mdash; Tea &amp; scones
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>2pm</span> &mdash; Speeches/Wedding breakfast
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>6pm</span> &mdash; Gather to start the party (+ cake &amp; pasties)
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>midnight</span> &mdash; Amps off, acoustic only
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>
        Sunday 10th September
      </h3>
      <p>
        <em>Wakey wakey</em> Breakfast on the Fire-pit &mdash; Provided for you, and prepared by the Man of Honour.
      </p>
      <p>
        Clean up &amp; tear-down.
      </p>
      <p>
        The celebrations officially finish at 3pm on Sunday.
      </p>

      {{#if contents}}
      <h2>A Final Note</h2>
      {{{md contents}}}
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="column">
      {{#unless rsvp}}
      <div id="rsvp" data-magellan-target="rsvp" class="typeform-widget" data-url="https://woody29.typeform.com/to/Oqko02?adult={{adult}}&children={{children}}&invitee={{invitee}}&a1={{is_ceremony}}" data-transparency="50" data-hide-headers=true data-hide-footer=true style="width: 100%; height: 500px;" > </div> <script> (function() { var qs,js,q,s,d=document, gi=d.getElementById, ce=d.createElement, gt=d.getElementsByTagName, id="typef_orm", b="https://embed.typeform.com/"; if(!gi.call(d,id)) { js=ce.call(d,"script"); js.id=id; js.src=b+"embed.js"; q=gt.call(d,"script")[0]; q.parentNode.insertBefore(js,q) } })() </script> <div style="font-family: Sans-Serif;font-size: 12px;color: #999;opacity: 0.5; padding-top: 5px;" > powered by <a href="https://www.typeform.com/examples/?utm_campaign=Oqko02&amp;utm_source=typeform.com-8602790-Basic&amp;utm_medium=typeform&amp;utm_content=typeform-embedded-poweredbytypeform&amp;utm_term=EN" style="color: #999" target="_blank">Typeform</a> </div>
      {{/unless}}
    </div>
  </div>

